ence the stories of the doings of the Lord, and repeats them every day, in not very long time, Lord enters the heart.","text2":"","created_at":null,"updated_at":null},{"id":20631,"chapterId":34,"type":"4-S","number":5,"lineNumber":1,"text1":"प्रविष्ट: कर्णरन्ध्रेन स्वानां भावसरोरुहम् ।","text2":"","created_at":null,"updated_at":null},{"id":20632,"chapterId":34,"type":"4-S","number":5,"lineNumber":2,"text1":"धुनोति शमलं कृष्ण: सलिलस्य यथा शरत् ॥५॥","text2":"","created_at":null,"updated_at":null},{"id":20702,"chapterId":34,"type":"5-B","number":5,"lineNumber":1,"text1":"प्रविष्ट: कर्ण-रन्ध्रेन","text2":"entering by the ear cavity","created_at":null,"updated_at":null},{"id":20703,"chapterId":34,"type":"5-B","number":5,"lineNumber":2,"text1":"स्वानाम्-भाव-सरोरुहम् ","text2":"of His devotees’, (into) the heart lotus","created_at":null,"updated_at":null},{"id":20704,"chapterId":34,"type":"5-B","number":5,"lineNumber":3,"text1":"धुनोति शमलम् कृष्ण: ","text2":"destroys impurities, Krishna","created_at":null,"updated_at":null},{"id":20705,"chapterId":34,"type":"5-B","number":5,"lineNumber":4,"text1":"सलिलस्य यथा शरत् ","text2":"of the water, like autumn","created_at":null,"updated_at":null},{"id":20817,"chapterId":34,"type":"6-E","number":5,"lineNumber":0,"text1":"Krishna enters through the ear cavity of His devotees and destroys the sins of their heart lotus, just as autumn clears the waters (of rivers etc.).","text2":"","created_at":null,"updated_at":null},{"id":20633,"chapterId":34,"type":"4-S","number":6,"lineNumber":1,"text1":"धौतात्मा पुरुष: कृष्णपादमूलं न मुञ्चति ।","text2":"","created_at":null,"updated_at":null},{"id":20634,"chapterId":34,"type":"4-S","number":6,"lineNumber":2,"text1":"मुक्तसर्वपरिक्लेश: पान्थ: स्वशरणं यथा ॥६॥","text2":"","created_at":null,"updated_at":null},{"id":20706,"chapterId":34,"type":"5-B","number":6,"lineNumber":1,"text1":"धौत-आत्मा पुरुष: ","text2":"a pure souled person","created_at":null,"updated_at":null},{"id":20707,"chapterId":34,"type"